            <h2 id="part-2" class="no-margins">
              Devices with a telecoil (T-coil) pick up the signal from a Hearing
              Loop and convert it into clear audio—delivering sound directly to
              the user without the need for extra equipment.
            </h2>
            <div class="spacer-sm"></div>
            <div class="section-divider home-c-numbers"></div>

            <h5>
              T-coil users can receive sound invisibly, simply and directly to
              their own hearing aid or cochlear implant without the need for a
              separate receiver.
            </h5>

